name: Free Underground Tekno Android App
short_description:
Free Underground Tekno Radio was born in Rome, Italy, the 1st of August 2008.
The web radio can't stop broadcast free tekno music all around the world.
Many people, artists, crews and sound systems joined Free Underground Tekno Radio and projects across time and countries.
Actually 3000+ performers published more than 6000 tracks in the Free Underground Tekno Soundcloud group with downloadable flag enabled ;)
We always supports T.A.Z., DIY culture, creative people and, of course, the freetekno music movement.
With this app You can listen Free Underground Tekno Radio wherever You are (Internet access required).
Your free access to gigabytes of underground original freetekno music and live shows on your mobile or tablet device.
http://www.freeundergroundtekno.org/
https://www.facebook.com/Free.Underground.Tekno.Radio
